        <div class="ASM-h3-Subheading clearfix colelem shared_content" id="u79846-4" data-muse-uid="U79846" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-IBE-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u79846-4_content" style="width:569px;margin-left:0"><!-- content -->
          <h1 id="u79846-2">GRAND PRIX AT CIRCUIT 500</h1>
       </div>   
       <div class="clearfix colelem" id="pu79797-13"><!-- group -->

        </div>
        <!-- /m_editable -->
        <div class="ASM---p---body-text clearfix grpelem shared_content left-block-1" id="u79797-13" data-muse-uid="U79797" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u79797-13_content"><!-- content -->
         <p id="u79797-2">Montréal is known for its many high profile festivals, like the International Jazz Festival, the Just for Laughs Festival and most importantly, the Formula 1 Grand Prix race. Looking for thrills, fun and excitement? </p>
         <p>Then join us at &ldquo;Circuit 500&rdquo;, a dream location for racing aficionados.  Relive Montréal&rsquo;s racing fever behind the steering wheel of your indoor kart. You will hear, smell and feel the action before each hair-pin  bend, and on every stretch. </p>
         <p id="u79797-5">This Grand Prix style race will pit 14 drivers to compete simultaneously in the quest for a pole position for the upcoming finals. Fans, bystanders and awaiting drivers will cheer, animate and electrify the ambiance and create the ultimate racing atmosphere. The event will start with one practice session of 5 minutes, followed by a qualification race of 10 minutes, which will qualify the 7 best drivers for the ultimate race. The Grand Prix will feature the 14 best drivers (7 from the first flight + 7 seven from the second flight) in a 15 minute race-off. </p>
         <p id="u79797-6">&nbsp;</p>
         <p id="u79797-8">Ultimately, the top three Grand Prix racers will each get to mount the podium and all drivers will obtain his or her performance sheet with their overall position and fastest lap!</p>
         <p id="u79797-9">&nbsp;</p>
         <p id="u79797-11">Lunch will be served at the end of the final race.</p>
         <p id="u79797-9">&nbsp;</p>
         <p>Duration of tour, including lunch: 5 hours </p>


        </div>
